articles.title: Japanese Yen Craters after BoJ Fails to Appease Bears, USD/JPY & EUR/JPY Soar - DailyFX
articles.description: The Japanese yen tanks on Tuesday, sending USD/JPY and EUR/JPY sharply higher after Bank of Japan’s monetary policy announcement fails to live up to market expectations.
